  "sections": {
    "Background": {
      "text": "Well-recognized complication of gastric bypass\nRapid post-prandial gastric emptying, release of gastric hormones, splanchnic vasodilation\nHyperinsulinemic and hypoglycemic state",
      "subsections": {},
      "tables": [],
      "links": []
    },
    "Clinical_Features": {
      "text": "Nausea/vomiting\n, bloating,\nabdominal cramps\n,\ndiarrhea\n, diaphoresis\nEarly dumping= symptoms 30-60min after a meal\nLate dumping= symptoms 1-3 hours after a meal",
      "subsections": {},
      "tables": [],
      "links": []
    },
